Overview

Demonstrates Lead Operating System replay and recovery behavior following a controlled processing failure.

The recording validates replay governance, recovery controls, audit logging, and successful operational restoration.

Recording Objectives

Demonstrate:

Lead creation

Lead processing

Controlled failure

Replay queue population

Replay execution

Successful recovery

Audit updates

Final completion
Recording Flow
Section 1

Lead Intake

Show:

Lead intake processing

Pipeline updates

Event logging
Section 2

Lead Process / Outbound

Show:

Record progresses

Controlled failure occurs

Failure recorded
Section 3

Replay Governance

Show:

Replay Queue update

Replay status

Attempt count

Replay execution
Section 4

Recovery

Show:

Successful replay

Audit update

State correction

Final completion
Success Criteria

Visible evidence of:

Lead_ID continuity

Correlation_ID continuity

Replay queue population

Replay execution

Recovery success

Final completed state
